---
---

<div class="quote">
  <span class="tag">— Source Tape</span>
  <blockquote>
    "Bitcoin brings to the world<br />rules without rulers."
  </blockquote>
  <span class="author">A. Antonopoulos</span>
</div>

<style>
  .quote {
    max-width: 460px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    padding: 1.75rem 0;
    border-top: 0.5px solid #1f1f1f;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid #1f1f1f;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .quote .tag {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.35em;
    color: var(--dim);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
  }
  .quote blockquote {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--fg);
    font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }
  .quote .author {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 0.9rem;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-style: normal;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .quote blockquote { font-size: 15px; }
  }
</style>
